tracks.name: ENDORPHIN
tracks.description: Wave music had it's influence on me and I continued developing my skill with this genre. It feels like a mix of heavy trap and ambient. Emotional and loud.

tracks.name: ACCELERATE
tracks.description:
I got into Wave and made this track in the style of classic Hardwave. This was actually made in one big rush of inspiration over only a few days.
Not my proudest work, but I learnt a lot.

tracks.name: two eyes open, welcome
tracks.description:
This was my first ever track. I wanted to go with something simple so this is a very atmospheric and thoughtful track that was
meant to set the mood for my entire project.
